```</p>

<p>This is pretty misleading because when generating a  element, second function argument ("$value") is not the value of generated  nodes, but the text of  node, whereas first argument ("$option") is indeed the value of generated  nodes.</p>

<p><em>Example:</em> $element-&gt;addMultiOption('choice1', 1)
<em>Expected result:</em> choice1<em>Actual result:</em> 1</p>

